{"tid":285130,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己係情感既寄生蟲","createTime":"2017-06-15T13:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T15:53:56.000Z","uid":63580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7506505cfd7440befd35db97f9e4987eafa6d891","tid":285130,"uid":63580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:49:07.000Z","msg":"男朋友工作好忙 佢有佢自己既圈子同朋友<br />\n唔係成日得閒理到我 有時候佢會用原先可以用來陪到我既時間來陪佢自己既朋友 我知道佢應該要有自己既正常社交活動 但我總覺得有種唔被重視既感覺 覺得佢排所有野既priority都高過我 然而自己係nothing's <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一方面 自己既朋友圈子都係咁 佢地各有自己既另一半 自己既工作 自自然然都唔會好似以前咁揾得我咁密 <br />\n<br />\n電話好靜 好幾個鐘都無人揾我 無人理我既時候 我就覺得好似比全世界捨棄咁 咁樣患得患失咁生活真係好痛苦 可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點樣先可以唔好咁依賴人地"},{"pid":"eab098a02ed406489167e5b7c048b379bdc3b5fe","tid":285130,"uid":29175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"試下搵下其他野做 整到自己好忙 或多或少可以分散自己注意力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但治本方法都係唔好太過依賴啦"},{"pid":"441936533a17008e017e6e846d799d71b618d977","tid":285130,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:05:46.000Z","msg":"pmed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6ec6fc4fec1326b432c01304473d29ce1787d0","tid":285130,"uid":69256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"總係覺得無人需要我⁠⁠⁠⁠"},{"pid":"dd4842b639c6678329077adfec690263b197e07b","tid":285130,"uid":63580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總係覺得無人需要我⁠⁠⁠⁠</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nSame here <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0cf4e8726b475b14e1515fc99605cc1d321682","tid":285130,"uid":91104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"有巴絲打需要你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}